high_descs: Turn around, proceed across to counter.  Turn right, proceed to sink.  Turn left to face sink.
Pick up potato from back of sink, behind tomato.
Open refrigerator, put on shelf above tomato, close refrigerator.  Wait four seconds.  Open refrigerator, remove potato, shut door.
Turn right, go to garbage can on left.  Turn left to face garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Pick up potato from sink area, put in refrigerator to cool, put in garbage.

high_descs: Turn around and walk ahead to the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge on the shelf above the tomato, in the same approximate place. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Take a step right and ahead to face the trash bin.
Place the potato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato in the trash.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the potato in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the trashcan by the refrigerator.
Throw the potato in the trashcan.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the trashcan.
